around money that you

00:00:31.100 --> 00:00:33.150 align:middle line:10%
would like the
opportunity to clear?

00:00:33.150 --> 00:00:37.050 align:middle line:10%
Well, this is what we're talking
about today, "The Law of Divine

00:00:37.050 --> 00:00:40.200 align:middle line:10%
Compensation," and joining me
to facilitate this conversation

00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:43.610 align:middle line:10%
