00:26:03.727 --> 00:26:04.560 align:middle line:10%
>>WILLIAMSON: Right.

00:26:04.560 --> 00:26:05.070 align:middle line:10%
>>LISA: It physically does.

00:26:05.070 --> 00:26:06.840 align:middle line:84%
