00:26:47.870 --> 00:26:49.329 align:middle line:10%
I have a wall in
front of my heart.

00:26:49.329 --> 00:26:49.828 align:middle line:10%
Why?

00:26:49.828 --> 00:26:51.960 align:middle line:84%
Because I have a wall in
front of my heart to you.

