your story around this.

00:32:07.690 --> 00:32:09.190 align:middle line:10%
>>WILLIAMSON: It
was many years ago.

00:32:09.190 --> 00:32:13.910 align:middle line:10%
I think it was in the 1980s,
and I was lecturing here

00:32:13.910 --> 00:32:15.510 align:middle line:10%
weekly in Los Angeles.

00:32:15.510 --> 00:32:18.180 align:middle line:10%
And I decided to do
an evening of a mix

00:32:18.180 --> 00:32:21.124 align:middle line:10%
of spiritual conversation
and musical entertainment,

00:32:21.124 --> 00:32:22.540 align:middle line:10%
and I thought it
was a great idea.

00:32:22.540 --> 00:32:26.380 align:middle line:10%
And actually, it was great,
except marketing genius that I

00:32:26.380 --> 00:32:30.380 align:middle line:10%
was not, I decided not to
really tell people what it was.

00:32:30.380 --> 00:32:32.600 align:middle line:10%
I wanted to surprise
them once they got there,

00:32:32.600 --> 00:32:36.189 align:middle line:10%
so I would tell people-- the
dumbest idea-- I told people

00:32:36.189 --> 00:32:37.730 align:middle line:10%
in my lecture, you
really want to go,

00:32:37.730 --> 00:32:39.046 align:middle line:10%
but I didn't describe it.

00:32:39.046 --> 00:32:41.420 align:middle line:10%
I didn't know how to say, it's
going to be so incredible.

00:32:41.420 --> 00:32:42.220 align:middle line:10%
Right.

00:32:42.220 --> 00:32:44.610 align:middle line:10%
As a consequence, not all
that many people came,

00:32:44.610 --> 00:32:46.580 align:middle line:10%
and I had rented
this big theater.

00:32:46.580 --> 00:32:48.547 align:middle line:10%
And everybody who was
there said, oh, my God,

00:32:48.547 --> 00:32:51.130 align:middle line:10%
if I'd known how great it was,
I would have brought 10 people.

00:32:51.130 --> 00:32:52.930 align:middle line:10%
It just broke my heart.

00:32:52.930 --> 00:32:56.130 align:middle line:10%
So my father and mother
had flown in from Houston.

00:32:56.130 --> 00:33:00.050 align:middle line:10%
And my father comes backstage,
little sister, it was great.

00:33:00.050 --> 00:33:03.440 align:middle line:10%
And I burst into tears, and
I said, daddy, it was a bomb.

00:33:03.440 --> 00:33:05.320 align:middle line:10%
He said, what do you
mean it was a bomb?

00:33:05.320 --> 00:33:10.250 align:middle line:10%
I said, I lost $10,000.

00:33:10.250 --> 00:33:12.620 align:middle line:10%
His response to me was,
oh, hell, little sister.

00:33:12.620 --> 00:33:16.620 align:middle line:10%
First of all, he said,
I'm really proud of you

00:33:16.620 --> 00:33:18.902 align:middle line:10%
that you made $10,000
that you could risk.

00:33:18.902 --> 00:33:20.860 align:middle line:10%
He said and I'm proud of
you that you risked it

00:33:20.860 --> 00:33:22.220 align:middle line:10%
on something wonderful.

00:33:22.220 --> 00:33:24.360 align:middle line:10%
He said if somebody
gives you a problem,

00:33:24.360 --> 00:33:27.660 align:middle line:10%
you just tell them I
can absorb the loss.

00:33:27.660 --> 00:33:30.192 align:middle line:10%
You just tell them you
can absorb the loss.

00:33:30.192 --> 00:33:32.400 align:middle line:10%
So in the days after that,
there was a friend of mine

00:33:32.400 --> 00:33:35.060 align:middle line:10%
who was in the show,
a woman named, Toni.

00:33:35.060 --> 00:33:38.430 align:middle line:10%
And Toni was,
because she loves me,

00:33:38.430 --> 00:33:40.930 align:middle line:10%
horrified that
I've lost $10,000,

00:33:40.930 --> 00:33:42.350 align:middle line:10%
