00:33:42.350 --> 00:33:45.137 align:middle line:10%
Well, her upset would
only increase mine.

00:33:45.137 --> 00:33:46.220 align:middle line:10%
>>LISA: And make it worse.

00:33:46.220 --> 00:33:47.969 align:middle line:10%
>>WILLIAMSON: So I
would say to her, Toni,

00:33:47.969 --> 00:33:49.200 align:middle line:10%
I can absorb the loss.

00:33:49.200 --> 00:33:50.790 align:middle line:10%
Toni, I can absorb the loss.

00:33:50.790 --> 00:33:53.040 align:middle line:10%
So now whenever anything
like that would happen to me,

00:33:53.040 --> 00:33:56.610 align:middle line:10%
and any time I meet
somebody, you just declare,

00:33:56.610 --> 00:33:59.340 align:middle line:10%
