00:41:12.682 --> 00:41:14.640 align:middle line:10%
>>LISA: Oh, yeah, break
that down a little bit.

00:41:14.640 --> 00:41:15.460 align:middle line:10%
>>WILLIAMSON: OK.

00:41:15.460 --> 00:41:19.900 align:middle line:10%
If I identify with higher
thought forms of love,

00:41:19.900 --> 00:41:23.210 align:middle line:10%
I am standing my ground
in the spiritual universe,

00:41:23.210 --> 00:41:24.760 align:middle line:10%
because the
spiritual universe is

00:41:24.760 --> 00:41:26.520 align:middle line:10%
that which emanates from love.

00:41:26.520 --> 00:41:29.020 align:middle line:10%
And then I am
under the laws that

00:41:29.020 --> 00:41:32.060 align:middle line:10%
prevail within a
world that loves me,

00:41:32.060 --> 00:41:35.110 align:middle line:10%
and which is invested in my
higher good and the higher good

00:41:35.110 --> 00:41:37.940 align:middle line:10%
of all living things
past, present, and future.

00:41:37.940 --> 00:41:40.080 align:middle line:10%
It's counterintuitive,
but the way

00:41:40.080 --> 00:41:45.370 align:middle line:10%
to have effectiveness and
power within the material plane

00:41:45.370 --> 00:41:49.030 align:middle line:10%
is to know that you're
not of the material plane.

00:41:49.030 --> 00:41:52.160 align:middle line:10%
The material plane is ruled
by lower thought forms.

00:41:52.160 --> 00:41:54.920 align:middle line:10%
Thought forms of
fear, ain't it awful,

00:41:54.920 --> 00:41:57.990 align:middle line:10%
scarcity, doubt,
it'll never happen,

00:41:57.990 --> 00:41:59.777 align:middle line:10%
it's all gone to hell
in a hand basket.

00:41:59.777 --> 00:42:00.360 align:middle line:10%
>>LISA: Right.

00:42:00.360 --> 00:42:02.780 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAMSON: And if that's
the world you identify with,

00:42:02.780 --> 00:42:04.790 align:middle line:90%
then that will be your reality.

00:42:04.790 --> 00:42:07.310 align:middle line:84%
That's where spirituality
becomes so important.

00:42:07.310 --> 00:42:08.410 align:middle line:90%
Who are you?

00:42:08.410 --> 00:42:09.520 align:middle line:90%
We are mortal beings.

00:42:09.520 --> 00:42:11.270 align:middle line:10%
We are material
beings, but the point

00:42:11.270 --> 00:42:12.990 align:middle line:10%
is that we are so
much more than that.

00:42:12.990 --> 00:42:15.869 align:middle line:10%
This is like a precious,
priceless suit of clothes

00:42:15.869 --> 00:42:16.660 align:middle line:10%
that we're wearing.

00:42:16.660 --> 00:42:19.520 align:middle line:10%
That's what the body is,
but this is not who we are.

00:42:19.520 --> 00:42:22.920 align:middle line:10%
That's why enlightenment is
the answer to everything.

00:42:22.920 --> 00:42:27.710 align:middle line:10%
Enlightenment is the realization
that the birth of the body

00:42:27.710 --> 00:42:30.330 align:middle line:10%
was not the beginning,
it was the continuation.

00:42:30.330 --> 00:42:32.130 align:middle line:10%
The death of the body
will not be an end.

00:42:32.130 --> 00:42:33.510 align:middle line:10%
It's a continuation.

00:42:33.510 --> 00:42:35.890 align:middle line:10%
You and I are not trapped
here in our bodies.

00:42:35.890 --> 00:42:38.790 align:middle line:84%
We are part of a
larger order of things,

00:42:38.790 --> 00:42:42.120 align:middle line:84%
and it's just like when
Jesus said in the Sermon

00:42:42.120 --> 00:42:44.890 align:middle line:84%
on the Mount, "Did God not
cloth the lilies of the field?

00:42:44.890 --> 00:42:47.350 align:middle line:10%
Surely, he will
take care of you."

00:42:47.350 --> 00:42:51.070 align:middle line:10%
And there are objective,
discernible laws

00:42:51.070 --> 00:42:53.325 align:middle line:10%
of the internal
universe just as there

00:42:53.325 --> 00:42:55.840 align:middle line:10%
are objective, discernible
laws of the external universe.

00:42:55.840 --> 00:42:59.240 align:middle line:10%
If I drop this book, I know
that it will fall to the ground.

00:42:59.240 --> 00:43:01.410 align:middle line:84%
This is not because I
have faith in gravity.

00:43:01.410 --> 00:43:03.820 align:middle line:84%
It's because I understand
the laws of gravity.

00:43:03.820 --> 00:43:05.020 align:middle line:90%
And same with love.

00:43:05.020 --> 00:43:07.947 align:middle line:10%
If my heart is open,
miracles will happen.

00:43:07.947 --> 00:43:09.280 align:middle line:10%
>>LISA: That is a great example.

00:43:09.280 --> 00:43:11.829 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAMSON: And when
I close, it won't.

00:43:11.829 --> 00:43:13.620 align:middle line:84%
You know, it's like
with spiritual exercise

00:43:13.620 --> 00:43:16.280 align:middle line:84%
and you say how to, how to,
you do spiritual exercise

00:43:16.280 --> 00:43:17.810 align:middle line:84%
